        </introduction>
        </exercise>
    <task workspace="0.01in">
        <statement>
            <p>
                Write a function <m>C</m> whose input is <m>x</m> is the temperature in Celsius degrees, and whose output is the temperature in Fahrenheit degrees.
            </p>
